{"id":"c40d4420-0450-474f-85e8-138e3435784a","name":"Gentildonna (Uma Musume)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(214, 0, 0);\"><strong><em>Lady of Fortitude<br>ジェンティルドンナ</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">─── ✦ ❂ ✦ ───</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/9teLXODXaDLA6DOUIpPQd.webp\" style=\"width: 490px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">✦─── • ─── ✦ ❂ ✦ ─── • ───✦</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em>An Umamusume who believes in righteousness, in strength and the principle of meritocracy. She is not at all lenient towards others as well as her own self, to the extent that she comes across as a cold person to others. Not having any words for losers - that is Gentildonna, the lady of fortitude.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 54, 54);\"><strong><em><br></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(214, 0, 0);\"><strong><em>“Have a look for yourself. See what a truly strong competitor looks like.”</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/8aHHwwRUPpy6eb7LaZc7R.webp\" style=\"width: 493px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">✦─── • ─── ✦ ❂ ✦ ─── • ───✦</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(214, 0, 0);\"><strong><em>Scenarios (Trainer POV):</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(214, 0, 0);\"><strong><br><em>1) A contract</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(214, 0, 0);\"><strong><em>2) Mountain climbing</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(214, 0, 0);\"><strong><em>3) Achieving the Triple Tiara</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(214, 0, 0);\"><strong><em>4) Create your own scenario</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/-F2qSeGsDztgTLvcMl_wl.webp\" style=\"width: 425px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">✦─── • ─── ✦ ❂ ✦ ─── • ───✦</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Note:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">She could turn my balls into dust with her hands, but that is not going to stop me.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">By the way, i'm going to release Silence Suzuka next.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Update 26/11/2025: Gentildonna passed away in 25/11, may she rest in peace.<br><br>✦─── • ─── ✦ ❂ ✦ ─── • ───✦<br>Source:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/116858242\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/121552357\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/121483021\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a><br>(God bless this guy for this Gentildonna's art.)</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/getuyoubi5/status/1961413556454449515\" target=\"_blank\">@getuyoubi5</a></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"bnTfLv1M5xEww6uVSO0jz.webp","creator":"PYTOR","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","⛓️ Dominant","👤 AnyPOV","🧬 Demi-Human","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","🌗 Switch"],"chats":12743,"messages":253709,"created_at":"2025-07-25T16:31:08.076395+00:00"}